title: Nihilism: Living as if Santa Claus Isn't Watching.
description: A very spontaneous (but also personal and profound) discussion on issues surrounding religion, disillusionment, death, the relationship between virtue and belief —and, in general, how life changes when you no longer believe that Santa Claus is watching.
